{"tid":1534230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"九月七去機場九月七去機場九月七去機場","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T15:22:03.000Z","uid":20856,"like":51,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"57e93699374157f312a0959be0f3660a6885ad74","tid":1534230,"uid":20856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:07.000Z","msg":"去圍太子把撚啊？市區佢話清就清話拉就拉，機場呢，咁多次行動入面拉嘅人最少，效果亦最大。<br />\n<br />\n九月七去機場！"},{"pid":"536c9688e1fa4c84cb300e1fab2461cbda398af4","tid":1534230,"uid":20856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:21.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"852ec08688dfb8d6f8e0fd8c9a6c7d25ed810171","tid":1534230,"uid":20856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"74822919ae8c618581e225f8b1737df82b4873dd","tid":1534230,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=444e1387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"af340e37db4378ade10c05ff3db4e19f2ab14d8c","tid":1534230,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a92d55ca321b0f232af5101ef51c4eeaaa76653","tid":1534230,"uid":20856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:45.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"c6440f8604ab8de7063cb3de44e7855e491e7f96","tid":1534230,"uid":20856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:57.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"4bef62f07492100f285ce548f838a6c6ed328507","tid":1534230,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b7cd184352dfb58e36997037bc5fc13143ede62","tid":1534230,"uid":285855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:50:59.000Z","msg":"香港回歸未定案嫁<br />\n<br />\n借一下位, 純手動po請見諒<br />\n<br />\n侵侵叫大陸還清朝債卷<br />\n大陸唔肯還成10萬億美金<br />\n佢話前朝唔認佢要還<br />\n如果唔駛還唔認點解要還香港<br />\nbloomberg同台灣都有講, 點解香港無聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n如果借據美國買左我地係美殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-29%2Ftrump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=651be60d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D