05a17fb07176d1803d","tid":1534230,"uid":64175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:26:21.000Z","msg":"五大條件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我要真雙普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5e130a306183bc0f14cf2237f9a68f4184e8e6","tid":1534230,"uid":186640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:27:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e885cdb9598638702647651569760bd80826c121","tid":1534230,"uid":13514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:27:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2eb9f3cb833cc03782b8589f8cc6d17108b18fa","tid":1534230,"uid":283494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"講遠少少。軍事上有一個名詞叫作choke point， 中文可譯為咽喉位。例如，霍爾木茲海峽就是全球石油供應的choke point，因為波斯灣啟航的運油輪全經此海峽，其闊度最窄只有39km。 伊朗經常威脅出兵霍爾木茲海峽對抗美國。<br />\n<br />\n講返香港。機場出市區條路，由東涌至青馬大橋，任何一個位都係choke point，一堵就會阻塞血管，令機場內及東涌人無法散去，數十分鐘內更會觸發市區入機場條路來回都塞死埋，而因為公路上有大量國際人士及車輛，政府會很顧忌。<br />\n<br />\n如果示威者以貨運為癱瘓目標，咁示威者可以不處理機場快線及東涌線，留路俾遊客，順便留條路俾各界人士接送親友。"},{"pid":"9822c444593889490aa3fcc373f903f173663ec4","tid":1534230,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:44:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3ff92b21681b3564445b9c56254bce0ece710d9","tid":1534230,"uid":67553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T06:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f981ce45de58ad78653e0cec9b01e0c3c7393c","tid":1534230,"uid":20856,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"相信嗰班帶唔到風向星期六唔入機場嘅，會開始吹話唔入機場都得㗎，機場死位好難走㗎，荔景都塞到㗎之類，不斷放大22公里長征嚟嚇鬼大家，令大家就算去都唔好入到機場咁入。<br />\n<br />\n但我想提醒大家，要入就一定要至少入到東涌嘅原因，同遊客混雜埋一齊，就係我地最佳嘅保護色。"},{"pid":"5b99d170e58db7ac7e82522d7da24a93bd2f6e0e","tid":1534230,"uid":203019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94377d0c0f2f54e77d083803dd494808aa6ccab8","tid":1534230,"uid":8880,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T08:37:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d83a8e8c74b3615bdd47bf388508c1aa64cac801","tid":1534230,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:10:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧鳴而死 不默而生<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">同我推哂D行動post上去啊<br />\nkeep 住團火 </span></strong></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCJE9v5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCJE9v5.png&h=ab29b81a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50bda388c6669789f39d1ab6166e7a1e56ca5f13","tid":1534230,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T15:13:05.000Z","msg":"."}]}